HTML-Feature version 0.01
=========================

This module extracts some feature sentence from HTML.


INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

    perl Makefile.PL
    make
    make test
    make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

    LWP::Simple
    HTML::TokeParser
    HTML::Entities
    Statistics::Lite
    Encode
    Encode::Guess
    Data::Dumper

